      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SO VOGUE (1) finished fifth two runs ago then broke and finished a distant sixth over 2610m at Kapunda at the latest appearance. Likely to get all the favours from this nice draw. Beautifully placed and she should turn things around. SPOTLIGHT (2) finished fifth last start, beaten 22 metres at Gawler over 2070m. Capable of playing a major role so has to be respected. HAYOAK (3) found form and finished second two runs ago then came back to earth when she broke and finished a distant seventh over 2610m at Kapunda. Will enjoy a nice run from this favourable starting position. This doesn't look as hard so she is capable of turning things around. MOJITO MADNESS (6) could only finish ninth over 2200m at Kapunda most recently. Open to improvement and is in the mix.",
